title: Strawberry Cinnaroo By Zenith E-Juice
description: Strawberry Cinnaroo eJuice by Cloud Thieves E-Liquid is a delicious blend of your favorite Cinnamon Swirl Cereal topped off with Strawberry Frosting and Rainbow Sprinkles! Experience a perfect trifecta of breakfast, fruit and dessert goodness rolled into one terrific vape.
